<bibRefCitation author="CAMP, D. K." box="[404,540,1720,1744]" pageId="4" pageNumber="321" pagination="123 - 189" refId="ref3089" refString="CAMP, D. K. 1998. Checklist of shallow-water marine malacostracan Crustacea of Florida. In: Camp, D. K.; Lyons W. G. &amp; Perkins, T. H. (Eds.). Checklists of selected shallow-water marine invertebrates of Florida. St. Petersburg, FL, Florida Department of Environmental Protection. p. 123 - 189. (Florida Marine Research Institute Technical Report TR- 3)" type="journal article" year="1998">Camp, 1998</bibRefCitation>
